parameters:
Phew... I understand your passion. You've cleared the Trial
of Ice... I'll let this be my defeat.

In consideration of your unwavering love... I will grant you
my power... Laura.

\SE[9]W-Wait...! I should be the one receiving the
power...!!

That was dangerous... I was carried away by the momentum of
the moment...

Ah, let me correct myself... Luna Roa. I will grant you
power. Come over here for a moment.

I've been watching your battle, and it seems like you can do
anything... It would be more reasonable to focus on one
skill, right? So...

Frozen Slash!! \!This allows you to imbue your weapon with
the power of ice and attack! It's perfect for someone who
excels in both academics and martial arts like you!

\SE[5]Ah... um... \SE[5]I'm already doing that... so...
it's okay.
No way...!?\! Huh!? It's my star product...!?\

Well, it may be a bit plain, but how about Ice Aptitude!
With this, you can use ice magic with a 10% boost! It's
perfect for someone reliable like you!

\SE[51]I-I'm sorry... I can already do something similar, so
that too is a bit...
T-This is also no good...! The academy is progressing too...

W-Wait a moment... Let me think of something else... Umm,
for example...
